Title : Comet Mountain
Text : :''This article is for the peak in Montana, United States.  For the one on the Coast of British Columbia, see [[Comet Mountain (British Columbia)]].  For the similarly-named peak in Nevada, see [[Comet Peak]].
'''Comet Mountain''', 3113 m (10213 feet),<ref>[http://bivouac.com/MtnPg.asp?MtnId=15160 Bivouac Mountain Encyclopedia entry]</ref> is a [[mountain]] peak in the [[Pioneer Mountains (Montana)|Pioneer Mountains]] of the state of [[Montana]], [[United States]], located in [[Beaverhead County, Montana|Beaverhead County]]<ref>{{gnis|781543}}</ref> 42km northwest of [[Dillon, Montana|Dillon]].<ref>[http://bivouac.com/MtnPg.asp?MtnId=15160 Bivouac Mountain Encyclopedia entry]</ref>

